════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div id="announcement-banner" class="relative bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 via-fuchsia-500 to-pink-500 text-white text-center py-2.5 px-4 text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium">
  <span class="opacity-90">🚀 Introducing Sidekick v2 — now with multi-agent orchestration.</span>
  <a href="#pricing" class="ml-2 underline underline-offset-2 font-semibold hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity">See plans →</a>
